- message to engine/controller to shut it down
 - handled directly by engine
  - if shell has has_kill_switch
  - { api: -2 }
   - use unix signals
   -2 ^C - cleanup and quit
   -9 quit now, no cleanup
   -15 kill - same as -2 for wab
   - quit on 2, 3, 6, 15
   - others log and continue

  - should opo support that and send it on exit
  
- support for list with select
